summary: A Cute Wood Elf you can found in Skyrim World
descriptionHtml:
====================================README===================================
After several times experiment for Wood Elf face i decide to share mine to be enjoyed by other Nexus user here. This is originally work by L0n3llyw0lf and what i do just make it shape with up to date mods and another beauty face mods by another modders. Hope you enjoy it.
She is waiting outside Helgen Cave after opening. You are the one who\'s will decide which faction, guild, gods worshiping she will follow.

============================ENDORSE THESE FILES!============================
> XCE by Xenius http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2356 
> Coverwomen Option #2 by mrLenski http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563
> Goblin Eyes Begone by natalie73 http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=212
> Athletic-CBBE body by Valstein0 http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=563

NB: The hair mods i used is from another modders forums and i can\'t share it here but if you like them just for own use you can PM me.

For the Armour i used:
> Somewhat Skimpy DragonScale Armour by ketwaroo http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=5411
> DragonScale and Dragonplate Recolors by Shinokage http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2103
